/**
 * Simulates an upstream ERP/PIM sync that refreshes pricing, inventory, and
 * availability for the entire catalog.
 *
 * After this completes, call `revalidateTag('products', 'max')` so cached
 * page views are refreshed in the background without blocking the admin's
 * next visit (stale-while-revalidate).
